 kill us.</p>\n<p>Remember, MERS, is going to kill us.</p>\n<p>Remember, Zika Virus, is going to kill us.</p>\n<p>Remember, Covid-19, is going to kill us.</p>\n<p>Remember, the Covid Variant, is going to kill us.</p>\n<p>Remember, Monkeypox, is going to kill us.</p>\n<p>Remember, the Hantavirus is going to kill us....\nagain...</p>\n<p>Remember these diseases, so when they try to dust one off and recycle it to fear monger, you can call their bullshit. Because if it didn't kill us when medical science was worse, how can it kill us when medical science is supposed to be so much better?...</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 29, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2053614795841228950", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsPkpmJo", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 25, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "deport", "id": 8612184, "raw_content": "", "author": "Hammond", "created": 1778518912880, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Belleoffreedom", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsPkpmJo.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/GregoryKBovino/status/2053614795841228950", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Bovino on the soundbite \u201cdeport only the worst of the worst\u201d. It\u2019s actually code for de facto amnesty for the other 100+ million illegal aliens already here. It also messages the next wave it will attract.  ", "last_comment_created": 177851922